      CodeElement​(java.lang.String name, CodeParent parent, int modifiers)
      Constructor with name, fully qualified name, CodeParent and modifiers.
      Initializes the lists of CodeFields, CodeConstructors, CodeMethods, CodeTemplateBindings, CodeTemplateParameters, CodeInterfaces and nested CodeElements.
      Sets the qualified name to the name value since it is set afterwards.
